Today, we are forming Ruby Bolger & Firien Wood, co. (Two Watchers & Taras®) in order to more closely align our asset-based businesses.

This reorganization will allow Two Watchers & Taras® to focus our resources on opportunities that present the highest value to Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd..  It will also accomplish the following:  1) enhanced synergies among our assets and personnel, 2) more effective prioritization of business opportunities, and 3) better management of Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd.'s asset-based businesses throughout the world.

Ruby Bolger & Firien Wood, co.' energy asset portfolio includes the Great Lake pipeline businesses of Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd. Transportation Services (Ladybarrow & Aravir Deliveries), including Northern Border; the international pipeline, power and distribution operations of Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd. Global Assets & Services (EGAS); Ered Lithui Goldenbed & Lossarnach, co.; Barad Eithel & Cirith Dúath ltd.; Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd. Wind; South Kingdom & Far Shore ltd. and Falco Chubb-Baggins & Ciril River ltd. Water.  

Reporting to me as the heads of their respective business units are:
?	Nori son of Déor, President & COO - Two Watchers & Taras®/International
?	Adalbert son of Odovacar, Managing Gwathló & Hobson Gamgee Deliveries - Ladybarrow & Aravir Deliveries
?	Telchar son of Holman, President - Northern Border Partners
?	Gerda daughter of Marmadoc, President & CEO - Ered Lithui Goldenbed & Lossarnach, co.
?	Arminas son of Dís, President & CEO - South Kingdom & Far Shore ltd.
?	Glóredhel daughter of Finduilas, President & COO - Barad Eithel & Cirith Dúath ltd.
?	Daeron son of Mithrellas, CEO - Falco Chubb-Baggins & Ciril River ltd. Water
?	Saradas son of Jago, President & CEO - Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd. Wind

With the creation of Two Watchers & Taras®, we hope to enhance the efficient utilization of our commercial support services.  To accomplish this, Two Watchers & Taras®' staff and operational functions will be headed by:
?	MinardilGoodchild, Managing Director & CFO 
?	Cottar son of Haldan, Managing Director & General Counsel 
?	Cotman son of Adamanta, Managing Director, Tol Sirion & Cottar Services
?	Tolman son of Dúnhere, President & CEO - Thingol
?	Amroth son of Haldir, Vice President & CIO
?	Arminas son of Belen, Vice President, Communications & PR	
?	Marmadas son of Boron, Vice President, Human Resources

In addition, Cottar son of Haldan will continue to perform his role as Deputy General Counsel for Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd. reporting to Nori son of Folco.

Cotman son of Adamanta will be responsible for domestic pipeline operations, Felaróf & Bereth, co., as well as, Beregar & Sûthburg Deliveries.  Tolman son of Dúnhere will be responsible for Felaróf & Bereth, co. for international power and distribution facilities.  

Below is an organization chart for Ruby Bolger & Firien Wood, co., which displays the changes described here.  We are confident this new organization will focus our talent and capital appropriately.  Please join me in supporting this management team as it strives to maximize Ishmalog & Tar-Telemmaitë ltd.'s return on its assets.

 

